{"tid":326621,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《射鵰》揮低《賭城》 《踩過界》贏口碑輸收視","createTime":"2017-07-18T06:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T02:58:25.000Z","uid":41351,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b47016279032f98c6d88f29218301dd6a0d034a","tid":326621,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"無線公佈上周收視紀錄，內地劇《射鵰英雄傳》及《賭城群英會》收視平穩，《賭》劇平均收視錄得20點，《射鵰英雄傳》於上周五播出大結局，平均收視錄得25點，最高有27點。《射鵰》全劇平均收視24點，暫列2017年最高收視劇集第3位，第1位是劇集《親親我好媽》、《不懂撒嬌的女人》打入第2位。<br />\n<br />\n　　逢周六及周日播出的劇集《踩過界》，兩日分別平均收視錄得16點及19點，其實《踩》劇口碑不錯，可惜一周只播兩集，令收視未如理想。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/145836_e856c283af650cc50c96fc53b21636e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F145836_e856c283af650cc50c96fc53b21636e1.jpg&h=ff3dbc48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d155dd1ff14888aabf211bb205b6181f265ec8a1","tid":326621,"uid":17322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dd5389bfc152b26ca396cbe5e4648a885b2c68c","tid":326621,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:31:08.000Z","msg":"有贏過口碑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f69c39c1a122e3edfd1d05f37eec22c2e93902a","tid":326621,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9ad19ccfc3f85c79c0892e4d74ca42cc11b561a","tid":326621,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:02:16.000Z","msg":"事實證明, 其實香港人都唔係好抗拒大陸劇<br />\n<br />\n之前 琅牙榜 收視得12點, 原來係套劇真係唔掂"},{"pid":"c50b9a3d433670cf9c4a37a12815202e3928eae9","tid":326621,"uid":37524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實證明, 其實香港人都唔係好抗拒大陸劇<br />\n<br />\n之前 琅牙榜 收視得12點, 原來係套劇真係唔掂</blockquote><br />\n係條撚<br />\n只係香港人熟悉射鵰先接受套劇"},{"pid":"ab2f9